summary: This is a preset for my secondary character.
descriptionHtml:
I'm feeling slightly generous today, so I'm giving away two of my most beloved presets. Don't make me regret this...

[b]Both presets use the Breton race

[/b]I'm going to assume that those who download this know how to install Racemenu presets, so no tutorials here.

[b][color=#ff0000]Required mods:
[/color][/b]
Racemenu and its requirements obviously. 
KS Hair 400
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?]SG Eyebrows[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes of Beauty[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/62639/?]Empyrean Warpaints [/url](For Anu_older)


[b][color=#ff7700]Body/Face textures I use:[/color][/b]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?]SG Textures Renewal[/url], no scars.
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3563/?]Coverwomen[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/16731/?]Fitness Body[/url]


[b][color=#ff0000]Q.A.[/color][/b]

Q. Will you make followers out of these? 
A. Maybe. 

Q. ECE Version?
A. I've abandoned ECE for Racemenu, so, no.
author: Undivide
